---
title: Miso-Honey Beef Strip Poke Bowl with Sesame Roasted Carrot, Slaw & Peanuts
description: This blissful bowl rivals what you'd get at your local poke joint. All you have to do is sear some tender beef, pop the
carrot in the oven, then pile it on a bed of fragrant jasmine rice. Serve with crispy slaw for a crunchy kick!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/easy-pulled-sesame-chicken-poke-bowl-a833872e.jpg
